Located at level 1 in Mcarthur Central Queen Street adjacent to Kfc. Upstairs portion is having Monitors, Gaming Headsets, Vinyls, Dvd's, Blu Rays and other stuff. Down stairs has got Telephone Section, IT, Speakers, headsets, watches etc. One of the Jbhifi's  Finest team working here. They are welcoming, Knowledgeable, hard working and fun loving  people. Busiest time is from 12 to 2 Pm so if you want to thoroughly check the product and ask many questions so this time is not for you, choose other time slot. Sales people are always eager to give you hand and help you out, try them and you will not be disappointed. This Jb and its team is my favorite.

PLEASE shop elsewhere! I had bought a television and sound bar off them, months along the line the tv starts to play up, so I try and call the store, no body picks up for a while, and when they do they just transfer you to the tv department which stays on hold for more than an hour. *They do this on purpose* This would happen everytime they knew i called. Seeing as calling them doesn't work I had emailed them many times and have not had a response as of yet.  If there is a Good guys go there instead they are much better with customers.
